cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with speech recognition and language modeling. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with acoustic models for speech recognition. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses different approaches for building neural models. It could also be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with neural models and their performance.
